,"uid":268297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d19706502650dc7bb2f386c9df598b7c2ec13204","tid":1993993,"uid":70452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T19:36:20.000Z","msg":"出去見下世面，你老闆無左你唔會死<br />\n佢想你好都會想你出去闖下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"好唔捨得我老細姐：（好老細難求"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"唔番份工都可以保持聯絡<br />\n天下無不散之席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T03:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個真 前同事會番公司逗利是 食開年飯"},{"pid":"f01ca4ced6660c3958adb2f1f1575f764b3e9ce4","tid":1993993,"uid":348499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"咁如果老闆好人又肯加我人工係咪應該唔好走？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老闆對我好好<br />\n好到我覺得我出去一定接受唔到做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果一個唔好彩裁左我都唔知點搵工"},{"pid":"a9b5829683ea490efe319795339d029490f1faae","tid":1993993,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bcf58c5a8d4d37852a2d8bef36178542d79ee3d","tid":1993993,"uid":268297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efc52f274140fbd8431f6ac1e9aa608b7c9d1409","tid":1993993,"uid":147721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"返工為經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"但做得開心都緊要？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T04:14:00.000Z","msg":"睇你自己點衡量價格啫<br />\n例如 執垃圾可能你覺得污糟 但係比十萬你你會做得好開心<br />\n開心係有好多因素 人工其實都佔幾大份 尤其係就算你一開始好有興趣 你做落半年就會厭 到時候個開心最大因素多數係人工<br />\n總之記住 一般而言 返工為人工"},{"pid":"985bf8564a8df4806a555605d515a3049f0c8a6c","tid":1993993,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f01ca4ced6660c3958adb2f1f1575f764b3e9ce4","tid":1993993,"uid":348499